cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "TGMS: An Agent-Native Bi-Temporal Graph Management System"
message: "If you use TGMS, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Zhang
    given-names: Xiaofei
    affiliation: University of Memphis
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.2.0
date-released: 2026-07-20
abstract: >-
  A bi-temporal property graph store whose query surface is a small algebra
  of verified temporal operators exposed as tools to LLM agents, with a
  Planner-Executor-Verifier agent layer that machine-checks every claim in
  an answer against the execution trace that produced it.
